Provenance / upstream attribution
---------------------------------

projectM-rs is a Rust port and derivative work of components of the LGPL-2.1
projectM / Milkdrop visualizer and its expression-language library. It is NOT a
clean-room reimplementation: substantial portions were ported file-by-file from
the upstream C++ sources listed below.

Upstream projects (all LGPL-2.1):

  * projectM / libprojectM
    https://github.com/projectM-visualizer/projectm

  * projectm-eval (the Milkdrop / ns-eel expression language)
    https://github.com/projectM-visualizer/projectm-eval

Many source files in this repository carry a per-file header (`//! Port of ...`
or similar) that identifies the specific upstream subsystem or source file they
were ported or adapted from — for example `Audio/PCM`, `Audio/MilkdropFFT`,
`MilkdropPreset/PresetFileParser`, `MilkdropPreset/PerPixelMesh`,
`Renderer/Framebuffer`, and others. Those headers are retained as provenance and
should not be removed.

As a derivative work, projectM-rs as a whole is licensed under the LGPL-2.1
(see the `license` field in the workspace `Cargo.toml` and the COPYING file).

This project is independent and is not endorsed by, affiliated with, or approved
by the projectM maintainers.


Preset content
--------------

No third-party / community Milkdrop `.milk` preset packs are bundled or
distributed with this repository. Users supply their own preset corpus.
The small built-in fallback preset and the snapshot test presets are original to
this project.


